Class AbstractPartitionConsumer

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.dataset.lib.partitioned.AbstractPartitionConsumer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PartitionConsumer
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConcurrentPartitionConsumer

    public abstract class AbstractPartitionConsumer
extends Object
implements PartitionConsumer
    Abstract implementation of PartitionConsumer, which manages state persistence and serialization/deserialization before delegating to the abstract methods.

      • onFinish

        public void onFinish(List<? extends Partition> partitions,
            boolean succeeded)
        Description copied from interface: PartitionConsumer
        This method must be called on any partitions returned by the #consumePartitions method. If a program fails to call this method for any partitions, those partitions will be 'expired' after a timeout defined on the configured ConsumerConfiguration.
